This pie is delicious! I used Pam on the bottom of the pie pan and didn't have any trouble getting it out of the pan. The curd will take at least 15 minutes to cook (not the 8 listed ine the recipe.) I made the curd two days ahead and the meringue the night before. A few quick minutes in the oven and the pie was ready to serve for Easter dinner.

